name: The Moon Cocktail Table by Kelly Hoppen - Davidson
description: The Moon Cocktail Table, a pinnacle of elegance and craftsmanship from the exclusive Kelly Hoppen for DAVIDSON collaboration, stands tall at 550mm in height and 450mm in diameter—a centrepiece for your entertainment space. Crafted meticulously, it features an oak base with black stained anegre accents. Elevate your space with this testament to collaboration—a sanctuary of refinement.
